@Plasmmer: Realtime kernel with 192Kbps audio output and input. Also, make it home theater friendly for Kodi and Steam Big Picture mode. Include Transmageddon and cryptocurrency wallets. Make Kernel+GPU driver combinations easy to select and install like in Manjaro. Make webapps and Android apps integral to a native-like experience.

Make it installable with a compressed file you can decompress directly to a USB thumb drive, just like SteamOS is, because that makes the install process a breeze.

I might be asking for too much, but I hold interest in your project regardless.
